{"tid":501701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果直搗三星老巢 首家南韓Apple Store月底開張","createTime":"2017-12-17T06:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T06:51:05.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"18bf3fd2450107e3564d24138e93dcc10fe3aa94","tid":501701,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:26:42.000Z","msg":"專門追蹤蘋果動態的美國科技新聞網站MacRumors與南韓科技新聞媒體ETNews報導，蘋果繼今年在台灣與新加坡等地成立旗艦店之後，終於要在年底前反攻三星電子的大本營。<br />\n<br />\n根據首爾裝修業者的說法，南韓首家蘋果直營店預定本月30日周六上午在首爾江南區開張，與三星電子打對台。<br />\n報導指出，這家蘋果旗艦店的店面有兩層樓，位於江南熱鬧的街路樹街購物區，並可能成為蘋果全球第500家直營門市，而且店面裝修、店員招募及訓練都已經在11月完成。<br />\n屆時蘋果負責零售事業的資深副總裁Angela Ahrendts，可能親自主持開幕儀式。<br />\n報導指出，目前蘋果在全球有499家門市，第499家是11月開張的紐約布魯克林新門市，而第498家是在加州矽谷蘋果新總部Apple Park 2之內的蘋果Visitor Center。（劉煥彥／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171217/1260857/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171217%2F1260857%2F&d=CbnD%2Fe2fgdhdmOHQVZijsQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=527d10f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171217%2F1260857%2F&h=0264fd75\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171217/1260857/</a>"},{"pid":"c3bc2d67122dad3e4da08f41b5bb31b15e3a31dc","tid":501701,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:48:27.000Z","msg":"我d韓國朋友全部用蘋果機<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f9c724a22edc1902437e5677b83af6cf479276","tid":501701,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"416de1b480b058f03212946d8f2130c6c1afbbf1","tid":501701,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:50:53.000Z","msg":"Apple同Samsung咪又係合作關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6adbeeb0e3cffcd31c2df72a550957ddea94f9ad","tid":501701,"uid":50328,"like":0,"disli